L

LunarCalendar - Interface in it.matteoavanzini.moon
Defines 8 phases of moon in an enum type: New Moon, Waxing to first quarter, First quarter, Waxing to full moon, Full moon, Waning to second quarter, Second quarter, Waning to new moon A moon day is a value between 0 and 29, where 0 is the new moon 7 is the first quarter 15 is the full moon 22 is the second quarter
LunarCalendar.MOON_PHASE - Enum in it.matteoavanzini.moon
